{"tid":1754093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[投票率問題]死左嘅選民會點處理？","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:09:13.000Z","uid":311223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5457bcb23873186a68a5b5e61503bd32419789b4","tid":1754093,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:01:23.000Z","msg":"睇番個投票率大約有7成<br />\n<br />\n但係啲年紀大死左嘅選民係現有機制入面似乎唔會剔除，只少我睇唔到政府個生死註冊處會咁醒目識得通知選民登記處去del record.<br />\n<br />\n咁所以實際投票率扣除班死人之後可能其實係更加高？<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以講解下？<br />\n<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4386e2d3bb4c1890741dc0f8b3d82c7d87ad74f","tid":1754093,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"死咗，張身份證會打個洞。"},{"pid":"5b0c0a94516b0b13f628477fa2dbd2a0031f1fae","tid":1754093,"uid":276273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"仲有選舉名冊有個cutoff day，過日之前死會cut走。<br />\n但係cutoff day到選舉中間有成幾個月，中途死咗就仍然係名冊"}]}